    <Notice Locale="UK">
        <Text><![CDATA[
※ Please update in an environment where the Bluetooth connection is most stable.
* Please be careful not to update while in riding on vehicles, such as trains, or in environments where 2.4 GHz band radio waves such as Wi-Fi, microwave ovens, cordless phones and many other radio waves are intermingled.

※ Sony | Headphones Connect ※
Please update to the latest version before updating the main unit

[Update details in version 4.5.2]
[1] Enhanced security features of the system software.
[2] Improved other functions.

This update includes update content that had previously been applied to the above applicable models.

[Notes]
1) Software update takes about 60 minutes for Android or about 60 minutes for iOS.
Never turn the "Power OFF" during update download, data transfer and updating.
If you do, the unit may become unusable.
2) Perform update after confirming that the remaining battery charge is sufficient on the headphones and Android device (or iOS device).
3)Update may be unavailable if a Bluetooth Low Energy device (wearable device, smartwatch, etc.) is connected to the Android device (or iOS device). Perform update after disconnecting all Bluetooth devices other than this device from the Android device (or iOS device).

[How to check the software version]
Select [WH-1000XM3 Version] from the upper right menu of Sony | Headphones Connect application screen. 


